Title: I will do meta analysis of your data
Description:
A statistical analysis known as a meta-analysis integrates the findings of various scientific investigations. When there are numerous scientific studies that address the same issue and each one reports measures that are anticipated to have some degree of error, meta-analyses can be conducted. Based on how this inaccuracy is viewed, the objective is to apply statistical methods to determine a pooled estimate that is the closest to the unknowable shared reality.

DETAILS ABOUT THIS GIG

1. Literature search(using pubmed and cochrane library)
2. Data extraction
3. Results interpretation
4. Analysis plots for meta analysis

* Forest plot
* Funnel plot
* Meta regression
* Risk of bias

PLEASE CONTACT ME BEFORE PLACING AN ORDER
